OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla will
OL,7,Farrive in Washington DC on Monday for
OL,8,Fa four-day visit aimed at marking the
OL,9,F250th anniversary of American
OL,10,Findependence and strengthening the
OL,11,Fspecial UK-US relationship.
OL,13,FThat relationship has been under
OL,14,Fserious strain in recent months, with
OL,15,FUS President Donald Trump lambasting
OL,16,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer and other
OL,17,FEuropean allies over their reluctance
OL,18,Fto get involved in the war with Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
