OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FThe visit is the most important
OL,7,Fforeign trip of the King's reign so
OL,8,Ffar, but now has the added element of
OL,9,Fsecurity concerns following a shooting
OL,10,Fat the White House Correspondents'
OL,11,FAssociation dinner on Saturday evening.
OL,13,FThe historic visit, the King's first
OL,14,Fto the US as monarch, will mark the
OL,15,Fstart of celebrations marking the
OL,16,F250th anniversary of the signing of
OL,17,Fthe Declaration of Independence, which
OL,18,Ffollowed forces led by George
OL,19,FWashington's defeat of King George
OL,20,FIII's army.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
