OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FUS First Lady Melania Trump has led
OL,12,Fthe preparations for the state visit,
OL,13,Fand highlights include Charles'
OL,14,Faddress to both houses of Congress and
OL,15,Fthe royal couple marking the 25th
OL,16,Fanniversary of the September 11
OL,17,Fterrorist attacks that brought down
OL,18,FNew York's Twin Towers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
