OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FIt is understood that following the
OL,7,Fshooting in Washington, there will be
OL,8,Fsome modest operational adjustments to
OL,9,Fone or two royal engagements during
OL,10,Fthe trip, but the overall plan remains
OL,11,Fas previously outlined.
OL,13,FSir Christian Turner, the British
OL,14,Fambassador to the US, said they were
OL,15,F"very confident that all appropriate
OL,16,Fsecurity measures are in place"
OL,17,Fregarding the royal visit.
OL,19,FHere's what we know so far.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
