OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FThe Trumps will welcome Charles and
OL,7,FCamilla to Washington on Monday, an
OL,8,Fannouncement by the First Lady's
OL,9,Foffice said at the weekend.
OL,11,FThe President and First Lady will
OL,12,Fgreet the King and Queen when they
OL,13,Farrive at the South Portico of the
OL,14,FWhite House on Monday afternoon.
OL,16,FBoth couples will then head to the
OL,17,FState Floor, where they will sit for
OL,18,Ftea in the Green Room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
