OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FAfter tea, Charles and Camilla will
OL,7,Fjoin the President and First Lady for
OL,8,Fa tour of the newly expanded White
OL,9,FHouse Beehive, which is nestled on the
OL,10,FSouth Lawn near the White House
OL,11,FKitchen Garden.
OL,13,FLater, the King and Queen will attend
OL,14,Fa garden party featuring guests
OL,15,Frepresenting the connection between
OL,16,Fthe US and UK.
OL,18,FThe royals will base themselves at
OL,19,FBlair House in Washington DC for the
OL,20,Fduration of their stay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
