OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FThe 120-room complex of four connected
OL,7,Fhouses is opposite the White House and
OL,8,Falso known as 'The President's Guest
OL,9,FHouse'.
OL,11,FTrump and Melania will host a State
OL,12,FArrival Ceremony on the South Lawn of
OL,13,Fthe White House on Tuesday morning.
OL,15,FDrawing upon a tradition that dates
OL,16,Fback to the 18th century, the couple
OL,17,Fwill mark the official arrival of the
OL,18,Froyals with a traditional military
OL,19,Farrival ceremony, which includes
OL,20,Fmilitary honours by the US Army Herald
OL,21,FTrumpets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
