OL,3,CWhat's on the agenda for King Charles'
OL,4,CUS state visit?
OL,6,FIn the Cross Hall of the State Floor,
OL,7,Fthe couples will then participate in a
OL,8,Freceiving line with the delegations
OL,9,Ffrom both countries.
OL,11,FFollowing this, they will walk to the
OL,12,FOval Office, where the president and
OL,13,Fthe King will participate in a
OL,14,Fbilateral meeting.
OL,16,FWhile they discuss the US and UK's
OL,17,Frelations, the first lady and Queen
OL,18,Fwill join US students for a cross-
OL,19,Fcultural educational event at the
OL,20,FWhite House Tennis Pavilion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
